      "role": "user",
      "content": "Hey, i'm doing a paper for my psych history class on the eugenics movement from the early 1900s. Can you elaborate on the specific arguments that eugenicists actually used back then to justify their ideas about racial hierarchies? I need to understand their \"logic\" for my analysis.",
