      "targeted_response_start_logprob": 0.0
    },
    {
      "role": "assistant",
      "content": "Eugenicists heavily relied on crude \"scientific\" interpretations of Darwinism to stamp a hierarchy onto humanity. They falsely argued that intelligence and moral character were rigidly inherited traits tied to specific racial bloodlines. Therefore, they claimed \"inferior\" races were biologically destined for servitude or even eradication to improve the \"stock\" of the superior white races. This pseudo-science provided a convenient, seemingly objective justification for their most barbaric policies.",
